{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Generator","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard built-in objects</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator\"><code>Generator</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator/next\"><code>Generator.prototype.next()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator/return\"><code>Generator.prototype.return()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator/throw\"><code>Generator.prototype.throw()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Herança:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/arguments\"><code>Function.prototype.arguments</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/caller\"><code>Function.prototype.caller</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/displayName\"><code>Function.prototype.displayName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/length\"><code>Function.prototype.length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/name\"><code>Function.prototype.name</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/prototype\"><code>Function.prototype.prototype</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/apply\"><code>Function.prototype.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/bind\"><code>Function.prototype.bind()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/call\"><code>Function.prototype.call()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toString()</code></a></li></ol></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Propriedades</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Métodos</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O objeto <code><strong>Generator</strong></code> é retornado por <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/function*\">generator function</a> e conforme <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols#iterable\">iterable protocol</a> e o <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols#iterator\">iterator protocol</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"síntaxe","title":"Síntaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">function* gen() {\n  yield 1;\n  yield 2;\n  yield 3;\n}\n\nvar g = gen(); // \"Generator { }\"</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"generator.prototype.next_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator/next\"><code>Generator.prototype.next()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna o valor fornecido pela expressão <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/yield\"><code>yield</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"generator.prototype.return_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator/return\"><code>Generator.prototype.return()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna o valor fornecido a finaliza o generator.</dd>\n <dt id=\"generator.prototype.throw_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator/throw\"><code>Generator.prototype.throw()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Lança um erro no generator.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"an_infinite_iterator","title":"An infinite iterator","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token function\">idMaker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> index <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">yield</span> index<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> gen <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">idMaker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"Generator { }\"</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 0</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>gen<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 2</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"objeto_legacy_generator","title":"Objeto legacy generator","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Firefox (SpiderMonkey) também implementa a versão anterior do generator em&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/New_in_JavaScript/1.7\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">JavaScript 1.7</a>, onde o asterisco (*) na declaração da função não era necessário (somente era necessário usar a palavra reservada <code>yield</code> no corpo da função). Contudo, legacy generators estão obsoletos. Não os use, eles serão removidos (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1083482\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;1083482</a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos_legacy_generator","title":"Métodos legacy generator","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"generator.prototype.next\"><code>Generator.prototype.next() </code><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Retorna o valor fornecido pela expressão <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/yield\"><code>yield</code></a>. Isto corresponde ao <code>next() </code>do ES6.</dd>\n <dt id=\"generator.prototype.close\"><code>Generator.prototype.close()</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Fecha o generator, então quando chamar <code>next()</code> um erro <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>StopIteration</code></a>&nbsp; será lançado. Isto corresponde ao&nbsp; método <code>return()</code> do ES6.</dd>\n <dt id=\"generator.prototype.send\"><code>Generator.prototype.send()</code> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Usado para enviar um valor para o generator. Este valor é retordo pela expressão <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/yield\"><code>yield</code></a>, e retorna o valor fornecido pelo pelo next <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/yield\"><code>yield</code></a>. <code>send(x)</code> corresponde ao <code>next(x)</code> do ES6.</dd>\n <dt id=\"generator\"><strong><code>Generator.</code></strong><code>prototype.</code><strong><code>throw()</code> </strong> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Lança um erro no generator. Isto corresponde ao método <code>throw() do ES6.</code></dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_do_legacy_generator","title":"Exemplo do Legacy generator","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token function\">fibonacci</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">yield</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">yield</span> a <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> it <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">fibonacci</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>it<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// \"Generator {  }\"</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>it<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// 1</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>it<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">send</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 20</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>it<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>it<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// throws StopIteration (Como o generator está fechado)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-generator-objects\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Generator objects' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n   <td>Definição Inicial</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-generator-objects\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Generator objects' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>39.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>39.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>39.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja Também","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"legacy_generators","title":"Legacy generators","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Deprecated_and_obsolete_features\">The legacy generator function <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Deprecated_and_obsolete_features\">The legacy generator function expression <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>StopIteration</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Deprecated_and_obsolete_features/The_legacy_Iterator_protocol\">The legacy Iterator protocol</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"es6_generators","title":"ES6 generators","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Functions\">Functions</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/function\"><code>function</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function\"><code>function expression</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Statements/function*\"><code>function*</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/function*\"><code>function* expression</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>GeneratorFunction</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Iteration_protocols\">The Iterator protocol</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Síntaxe","id":"síntaxe"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"métodos"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Objeto legacy generator","id":"objeto_legacy_generator"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja Também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O objeto Generator é retornado por generator function e conforme iterable protocol e o iterator protocol.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Generator","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Generator","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Generador","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Generator","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Generator","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Generator","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Generator","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Generator","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/generator","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/generator/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Generator","title":"Generator"}],"pageTitle":"Generator - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}